t. Kunlun's Qionghua School since a young age, Murong Ziying (慕容紫英).","collection":69,"franchise":1176,"franchises":[1176],"popularity":1.0,"developers":[14085],"publishers":[14085],"category":0,"themes":[17],"genres":[12,16],"first_release_date":1185926400000,"platforms":[6],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":6,"date":1185926400000,"region":6,"human":"2007-Aug-01","y":2007,"m":8}],"alternative_names":[{"name":"Chinese Paladin 4","comment":"Acronym"},{"name":"仙剑奇侠传四","comment":"Chinese title"},{"name":"仙劍奇俠傳四","comment":"Chinese title"},{"name":"Xiānjiàn Qíxiá Zhuàn Sì","comment":"Chinese title"},{"name":"Xianjian Qixia Zhuan 4 ","comment":"Chinese title"}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/kotfm6w1u0iurwk234hr.jpg","cloudinary_id":"kotfm6w1u0iurwk234hr","width":800,"height":600},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/xmgy5lfbek0prs3w21us.jpg","cloudinary_id":"xmgy5lfbek0prs3w21us","width":800,"height":600},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ohuhyiqj3cwxzgvjmcne.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ohuhyiqj3cwxzgvjmcne","width":1024,"height":768},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/vny7xtaimnxtolilf9hc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"vny7xtaimnxtolilf9hc","width":1024,"height":768},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/uvk6cry6jc9giwli7iki.jpg","cloudinary_id":"uvk6cry6jc9giwli7iki","width":1024,"height":768}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/azbytrrcmzwkg5swmfrc.jpg","cloudinary_id":"azbytrrcmzwkg5swmfrc","width":800,"height":1112},"websites":[{"category":3,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Legend_of_Sword_and_Fairy_4"}]},{"id":78466,"name":"The Legend of Sword and Fairy 3 Prequel","slug":"the-legend-of-sword-and-fairy-3-prequel","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/the-legend-of-sword-and-fairy-3-prequel","created_at":1513602216859,"updated_at":1513604223596,"summary":"This waizhuan (side-story) to the third game in Xianjian Qixia Zhuan series is not directly 