 if you like it! \n \n■ Over 20 Levels, and more coming soon! \nYou'll play through 20 short courses one after the other, with the courses changing each time you play. You'll find all kind of monsters on your way. \n \n■ Be ready to swim \nSome of the levels will require you to get into the water in order to carry on, be careful, water is freezing! \n \n■ Super Jumps \nGot stuck somewhere? Cannot reach the other side with a normal jump? watch out closely for jump propellers, they might be hidden, even underwater. \n \n■ Wold Map \nYou'll be making progress through a wold map, going one step forward on each level, and you can always go back to play again on any of the completed levels. \n \n■ Ranking \nGoogle Ranking integrated, so you can compete against your friends to see who is the boss. Hint: The quickest usually has an advantage :) \n \n■ Tutorial \nNot sure where to begin? Check out the tutorial and get up to speed within seconds. \n \n \n■ Support Skills \nNeed some help? Grab a healthy potion if you are struggling or use the armor shield to be more resistent against your enemies. Trying to beat your own records? Wear on the speed shoes and run faster than ever! \n \n■ Weapons \nHitting your enemies with a stick is good fun... but it's even better if you can drop and shoot bombs... and how about throwing them a boomerang? You'll find spare weapons through the levels, make sure you grab as many as you can, you might need them later on! \n \n■ Gold and Shop \nYou will be rewarded while you accomplish all your missions with gold of all kinds, which you can use to buy more weapons at the store. Run out? No worries, you can always purchase them as well within seconds. \n \n■ Active development \nPlease, note that while Jungle Monk is ready for you to crack on with it, we are actively working on it, and we are planning to bring in new features, levels and much more improvements. \n \n■ Feedback \nYour feedback is really appreciated, we will genuinely read all your feedback and we are looking forward to hearing from your the features that you would like to see in the game and we'll do our best to make them real. \n \nThank you for choosing Jungle Monk and have fun!","popularity":1.0,"games":[36792,26163,236,47823,37088,19289,26848,1221,24048,36534],"tags":[17,268435487,536871038,536872039,536873467,536873497,536887603,1073741828],"developers":[14177],"category":0,"player_perspectives":[4],"game_modes":[1],"keywords":[126,1127,2555,2585,16691],"themes":[17],"genres":[31],"first_release_date":1514073600000,"status":4,"platforms":[34],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":34,"date":1514073600000,"region":8,"human":"2017-Dec-24","y":2017,"m":12}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/wnjk2o3aytqb9ecyfrfd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"wnjk2o3aytqb9ecyfrfd","width":1026,"height":603},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/rwjc4wzkkc6e92bknnfe.jpg","cloudinary_id":"rwjc4wzkkc6e92bknnfe","width":1282,"height":801}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/qqqszrg55c4occqshqe7.jpg","cloudinary_id":"qqqszrg55c4occqshqe7","width":1280,"height":800},"websites":[{"category":12,"url":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.jungle.studio99"},{"category":8,"url":"https://instagram.com/instagram.com/globalnewsgames"},{"category":1,"url":"http://thedeveloperworldisyours.com"}]},{"id":78628,"name":"Wheels0","slug":"wheels0","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/wheels0","created_at":1514094175041,"updated_at":1514101049253,"summary":"An endless racing game that i made to learn the basics of unity via a Jimmy Vega tutorial. Enjoy!","storyline":"An endless racing game which you can play to see how far we are in our game development skills. Expect better games to come along the way as we grow bigger and better. Join us for the ride won't you?","franchise":1190,"franchises":[1190],"popularity":1.0,"tags":[1073741827,1073741826,1073741825],"developers":[14178],"publishers":[14178],"game_